Last Battle Was Tough, Sir. 

Seems Like We Only Have One Cannon Ball Left To Defeat The Enemy.

We Have To Bounce The Ball From One Side To The Other To Eliminate All The Foes, So It's One Time Use.

Our Engineers Strapped Bear Traps Onto The Paddles.

You Can Hold The Left Mouse Button For A More Accurate Shot, Sir.
Made For GJL Game Parade Summer 2021 By Cocco.
